{
  "texts": [
    "IntroductionChinese Sign Language is a particular expression that has its own characteristics, cultural significance, and aesthetic value.",
    "On the one hand, this expression combines the pronunciation and meaning of Chinese to teach and express.",
    "On the other hand, it expresses the meaning of Chinese in the form of gestures, uses hand movements to publicize Chinese characteristics, and expresses cultural aesthetics.",
    "Although the meticulous characters of Chinese have influenced the development of Chinese Sign Language, it still has its own characteristics and culture.",
    "It expresses the meaning of Chinese through quick gestures, forming an interesting way of expression."
  ]
}